    + TLC-035 candidates proposed)
  - docs/SPRINT_19_PLAN.md (next commit; Sprint 19 close)
  - tests/setup.ts applyMigrations (the function this commit hardens)
  - vitest.config.ts pool: 'forks' (the parallelism that produces
    the catalog race)

